criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Cerebellar ataxia

          -  Score > 1 ≤ 4 on posture of Scale for assessment and rating of ataxia

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals with other neurological disorders, postural hypotension, vestibular,
             visual, cardiovascular or musculoskeletal disorders that affect the performance of the
             proposed tests;

          -  Pacemaker;

          -  History of seizures;

          -  Metallic implants in the head or neck;

          -  Medication change (3 months) during the period of study
